{"tid":2487514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張翔：港大建校初心就是為中國而立","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T15:24:05.000Z","uid":127511,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3abcd65410ec202c20c6df83373d38145d147a17","tid":2487514,"uid":127511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX0yEPSDMfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrX0yEPSDMfQ&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=bca2d972\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX0yEPSDMfQ</a>"},{"pid":"fe63762f61c63d2c8f873ee245932558f924cb9b","tid":2487514,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"又係點新聞fake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feddc7bdd5fd0aff57393c36a3fa70a89713fa8e","tid":2487514,"uid":53062,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"為咗顛覆中國而成立"},{"pid":"f99e3012a1ecb4d256bd1f692ffd449723d8ab86","tid":2487514,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"feddc7bdd5fd0aff57393c36a3fa70a89713fa8e","tid":2487514,"uid":53062,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"為咗顛覆中國而成立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"革大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c7e6256769eb5d7a7a6dfb2e30af685180441d","tid":2487514,"uid":289480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3abcd65410ec202c20c6df83373d38145d147a17","tid":2487514,"uid":127511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX0yEPSDMfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrX0yEPSDMfQ&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=bca2d972\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX0yEPSDMfQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"港大建校初心是為使中國變成西方民主體制而立！"},{"pid":"58dfffba17381e5598289e7830edb8313ec51dad","tid":2487514,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"【大公報訊】記者張強報道：在開幕儀式上，香港大學校長張翔發表了以《新時代 新發展 新格局》為主題的寄語。他表示，港大在1911年建校時，其初心就是「為中國而立」，經過一百多年的發展，港大已經是國際化最成功的世界一流大學。今天港大北京中心的成立，是港大面向未來發展的一個新的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n  張翔指出，港大北京中心選址在亞投行總部的亞洲金融大廈，是北京中軸線的新地標，地理位置優越，吸引了大量的國際金融商業文化機構落戶，更因其互聯互通的理念與港大北京中心「立足北京 融入中國 擁抱世界」的目標一致。他希望中西交融的獨特定位，能夠讓港大北京中心成為內地與國際化教育共融的理想平台。一方面加強兩地在學術研究和行業實踐領域的合作和交流，另一方面為各類人才開拓國際視野，提供終生學習的機會。<br />\n<br />\n  張翔表示，他相信港大享譽國際的研究實力、世界頂尖的師資，以及強大的學術和行業夥伴網絡，能夠讓港大北京中心創造更多的教學研究和與社會各界合作的機會，更好地發展香港大學的優勢，以推動社會的可持續發展。他指出，目前社會各地飽受地緣政治、經濟角力和新冠肺炎疫情帶來的重重挑戰，在這個艱難的時期，更應該抱開放的態度，與時俱進、勇於創新；北京中心的成立正體現了香港大學在新時代的積極探索，冀共同抓緊機遇，開創新的未來。<br />\n唔好貼共產黨link<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd01e214d6842f85d25a16821e9d3af394f1087","tid":2487514,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"南京事件都只為中國而做<br />\n八國聯軍又樣只為中國而立"},{"pid":"b305947e9c7011bcc662eb2254432cf72da5b639","tid":2487514,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"一個持有綠卡嘅黨委書記講呢啲<br />\n真係難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"57f7061d702c191c8ee70d343a413bfda73ab9fb","tid":2487514,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"百年校譽玩完"},{"pid":"0f7e7087a9e90394bb1fb7d2f2d7219220390a43","tid":2487514,"uid":39181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"明明香港大學建校既目的係彰顯大英帝國喺遠東既威望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb7e2ded24c26f312da1bd0e501875cfec2638","tid":2487514,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"佢係咪撈亂咗中大同港大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003a0885ef79bf23d58df905bbfd13cbaf56548e","tid":2487514,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"玩偷換概念，又一證明呢條友又係食屎大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，無錯！係當時嘅&rdquo;中華民國&rdquo;  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98269043fb70349f9d5f5c7d4336cbbc60ea1c96","tid":2487514,"uid":305058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"港大有歷史啲<br />\n定中華人民共和國有歷史啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb707e2233537663f143f702f2dac9a890b904fd","tid":2487514,"uid":315372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"成立港大嗰陣仲係清朝咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0e0c52842851c34c58e218b64be500c1c6be48","tid":2487514,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"清朝？"},{"pid":"8e4981f7b62dc873ea399b118a0b10217fee7559","tid":2487514,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾點新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a730210e7c97345c0e01c0c26b4f1ebc50397c79","tid":2487514,"uid":363016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b305947e9c7011bcc662eb2254432cf72da5b639","tid":2487514,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"